{
  "stem": "18450.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 16.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "On the plantation, just my-- just my mother and I.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My brother they took away to the-- to work.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I guess it was in '42, or maybe '43, I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But he was a strong, tall guy, six foot tall, maybe more.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they took him away to work.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They said, you know, he was older than I was.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That-- and a few times, he came, you know, like they gave him a day or two.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He came and he brought us some bread, whatever he could save up.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that's all.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He didn't know himself.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I mean he didn't tell us where he is, what he's doing.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We did.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, we did, a little.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not-- we didn't know about the concentration camps.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We knew that they're killing Jews.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that thing is that the day they had radios outside on the streets.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But they didn't have, you know, in the villages.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[BACKROUND NOISE] And I was in the city.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I came up, and I hear that they say in Russian, our Army took over Kostopol, the city of Kostopol.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I was so excited.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I came home.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I run home, and told my mother and so.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But, you know, nobody paid attention.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Because it was so bad.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "That you really looked for a piece of bread or a little bit of soup, then politics weren't the main talk.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Nobody talked about politics.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I mean, your mind wasn't on this.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You had nobody to talk to there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because the people who were there, [? were ?] [?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Uzbek, ?] you know, the natives.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Their lives were different.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I'm not going to say they were bad.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But, you know, and sometimes they gave you something to eat.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know, sometime they brought up a piece of bread to eat.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
